headline: Does the Latest AppLovin Rally Signal More Growth Ahead for 2025?
summary: If you are holding AppLovin shares or thinking about your next move, you are not alone. The stock has been on an epic run that has grabbed attention across the tech space. Over just the last week, AppLovin jumped 16.4%, capping a stunning 65.9% gain so far this year. That is on top of a jaw-dropping 481.2% surge over the past twelve months.
